query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS coupon_usage (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  couponId INT NOT NULL,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  orderId INT,
  usedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_couponId (couponId),
  INDEX idx_userId (userId)
)
